page.name: Thyton's Request!
page.description: Thyton received some disturbing news. Another group of pirates from a neighboring island has sent chests of weapons along with support pirates! He has asked you to cut off the aid before it reached the Osprey Cove, and burn the crates.

properties.name: Thyton's Request!
properties.description: Thyton received some disturbing news. Another group of pirates from a neighboring island has sent chests of weapons along with support pirates! He has asked you to cut off the aid before it reached the Osprey Cove, and burn the crates.
properties.complete: Well done! You defeated the wave of reinforcements before they could reach Osprey Cove, and burned the crates of weapons to the ground, but more help will be coming! Prepare yourself hero!
